      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional automotive specimen, maintained to the highest standards of preservation. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality unit with an uncompromising service history and flawless aesthetic integrity. Every detail, from the factory-original finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a legacy of meticulous ownership. This is the definitive choice for the discerning collector who demands excellence without compromise.",
